description:
This is a 24 minute workout called 'MEET YOUR SPIRIT GUIDES (Guided Meditation) 528Hz' from the channel Rising Higher Meditation ®.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Meet Your Spirit Guide, guided meditation is designed to help you to get into an appreciative, relaxed state so that you can easily interact with the non-physical who is guiding you, supporting and loving you.
